分别来自区块链、生物疫苗、芯片、多晶硅、免税等。统计显示，以周为单位，截至7月31日，共有74股获融资客连续加仓6周以上。分行业看，这些股票主要来自医药生物电子、非银金融、化工、国防军工等行业，其中医药生物领域股票数量最多。</p><ul class=\"stockCard list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><a class=\"stockHref\" href=\"https://www.futunn.com/quote/stock?m=hk&code=HK0000186335\"><span class=\"stockInfo\"><span class=\"market HK\">HK</span><span class=\"sname\">嘉实中国A股研究精选(美元)</span><span class=\"timeInfo\"><span class=\"stockTime\">更新：2020/8/6</span></span></span><span class=\"stock-price\"><span class=\"rate-content\"><span class=\"rate green\">81.84%</span><br><span class=\"tips\">成立至今</span></span><span class=\"price-content\"><span class=\"price\">23.4580</span><br><span class=\"tips\">单位净值</span></span></span><span class=\"canvasBox\" chartdata=\"12900000000,12999000000,13066000000,12822000000,12973000000,13040000000,12996000000,13018000000,12979000000,13051000000,13068000000,13007000000,13252000000,13460000000,13521000000,13580000000,13539000000,13665000000,13798000000,13830000000,13863000000,13815000000,13873000000,13779000000,13796000000,13863000000,13772000000,13741000000,13727000000,13703000000,13770000000,13727000000,13765000000,13609000000,13591000000,13587000000,13555000000,13714000000,13912000000,14013000000,14095000000,14168000000,14181000000,14172000000,14132000000,14178000000,14250000000,14191000000,14178000000,14235000000,14279000000,14332000000,14450000000,14479000000,14529000000,14478000000,14460000000,14449000000,14607000000,14670000000,14626000000,14695000000,14877000000,14967000000,14842000000,14754000000,15002000000,14954000000,15155000000,15423000000,15408000000,14911000000,14830000000,14534000000,14647000000,14711000000,14435000000,14509000000,14641000000,14616000000,14492000000,14251000000,14501000000,14883000000,14654000000,14842000000,14871000000,14692000000,14669000000,14982000000,15077000000,15321000000,15281000000,15028000000,15173000000,15295000000,15608000000,15655000000,15667000000,15736000000,15698000000,15748000000,15800000000,15747000000,15943000000,160